Here is a multiple choice question in JSON format. Answer it based on the choices provided.

{
    "question": "Given the string s = \"Hello, World!\" you need to create a piece of code that will return a list of the words in s but in reversed order while preserving the original string. Which one of the following code snippets achieves this goal?",
    "choices": [
        {
            "choice": "```python\nreversed_s = s.split(' ')\nreversed_s.reverse()\n```"
        },
        {
            "choice": "```python\nreversed_s = ''.join(reversed(s))\nreversed_s = reversed_s.split(' ')\n```"
        },
        {
            "choice": "```python\nreversed_s = s.split(' ')[::-1]\n```"
        }
    ]
}
